{"tid":1737611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極重要！被捕後黃金48小時家人朋友須知！","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T09:21:29.000Z","uid":182994,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb6989a64e2a0365b971b26bbd50e928168cd44","tid":1737611,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"呢條link係被捕者家人須知 <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/127614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F127614&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=efb4d6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/127614</a><br />\n<br />\n務必要睇，暴動罪最高刑罰係十年，請細心閱讀以上須知。<br />\n<br />\n被捕者朋友同家人請兵分兩路，一批去警署搵，一批要係屋企清野，每一樣相關既野都係證據，一定要清理好，同時要想辦法處理被捕者既社交媒體，最好暫時刪除。切記，就算幾緊張都好，唔好同警察講任何野，警察會扮好人問屋企人攞料。家人同朋友要保持頭腦清醒，先可以幫到小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n清屋企既野同唔好同警察講任何野係重中之重。"},{"pid":"c993cc92f5b31dde21db5cab7b1528edcc06459d","tid":1737611,"uid":182994,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"仲有電腦要拎走"},{"pid":"68fda988cde4ac6ef3a409ed14cb66f248e107d4","tid":1737611,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d155f28e407f6537cb0f68a852b6f1d23bb9fee3","tid":1737611,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=aa990d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht